author: eTN Global Editor
title: AirAsia launches direct Kuala Lumpur-Sapporo flight
text:
AirAsia launches direct Kuala Lumpur-Sapporo flight Adv: 
Aug 02, 2015 Adv: 
KUALA LUMPUR, Malaysia - AirAsia X is to launch 4 times weekly direct flights between Kuala Lumpur and Sapporo, Japan, on 1 October 2015. 
To celebrate the launch, AirAsia X is offering promotional all-in-fares that are available for online booking starting until 2 August 2015 for travel between 1 October 2015 and 31 August 2016.
